<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>韓文學習App - Vocabulary Builder</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 30px;
    }

    /* Navigation (same as Home) */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.15);
      z-index: 1000;
      padding: 18px 0;
    }
    .nav-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #c084fc;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      color: #4b2e5a;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover,
    .nav-links a.active {
      color: #c084fc;
    }

    /* Hero / Header */
    header {
      padding: 160px 0 100px;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff5f0 0%, #ffffff 100%);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 4.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #c084fc;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      color: #6b21a8;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    /* Main Content */
    section {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      color: #4b2e5a;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    /* Daily Vocab Lists */
    .vocab-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(380px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 100px;
    }
    .vocab-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 40px 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .vocab-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(192,132,252,0.15);
    }
    .category-icon {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #d19fe6;
    }
    .vocab-card h3 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #4b2e5a;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .word-list {
      list-style: none;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }
    .word-list li {
      margin: 12px 0;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .korean {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #c084fc;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    /* Progress Tracker */
    .progress-container {
      background: #f9f9fc;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 50px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 100px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .progress-stats {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 60px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
    .stat {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #c084fc;
      display: block;
    }
    .badge {
      background: #fff0f5;
      color: #c084fc;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 16px 48px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      background: #c084fc;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(192,132,252,0.25);
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      background: #a855f7;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(168,85,247,0.35);
    }

    /* Footer (same as Home) */
    footer {
      padding: 80px 0 40px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #888;
      background: #f9f9fc;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    footer .accent {
      color: #c084fc;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 { font-size: 3.2rem; }
      .subtitle { font-size: 1.5rem; }
      .nav-links { gap: 24px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
      .progress-stats { gap: 40px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <div class="container nav-container">
      <a href="#" class="logo">공부하자 💕</a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="https://codepen.io/Yammi1119/full/JoRPrRB">Home</a>
        <a href="#" class="active">Vocabulary</a>
        <a href="https://codepen.io/Yammi1119/full/jEMNGVV">Resources</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>每日單字 • Vocabulary Builder</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">可愛又實用！每天5–10個單字，搭配圖片+發音+例句，讓你輕鬆記住韓文 💜 從食物到心情，全部陪你學～</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">今日主題單字</h2>
      <div class="vocab-grid">

        <div class="vocab-card">
          <div class="category-icon">🍜</div>
          <h3>食物 Food</h3>
          <ul class="word-list">
            <li><span class="korean">김치</span> - kimchi (泡菜)</li>
            <li><span class="korean">떡볶이</span> - tteokbokki (辣炒年糕)</li>
            <li><span class="korean">비빔밥</span> - bibimbap (拌飯)</li>
            <li><span class="korean">삼겹살</span> - samgyeopsal (五花肉)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="vocab-card">
          <div class="category-icon">✈️</div>
          <h3>旅行 Travel</h3>
          <ul class="word-list">
            <li><span class="korean">여행</span> - yeohaeng (旅行)</li>
            <li><span class="korean">공항</span> - gonghang (機場)</li>
            <li><span class="korean">호텔</span> - hotel (酒店)</li>
            <li><span class="korean">지도</span> - jido (地圖)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="vocab-card">
          <div class="category-icon">😊</div>
          <h3>情緒 Emotions</h3>
          <ul class="word-list">
            <li><span class="korean">행복해</span> - haengbokhae (幸福)</li>
            <li><span class="korean">사랑해</span> - saranghae (我愛你)</li>
            <li><span class="korean">피곤해</span> - pigonhae (累了)</li>
            <li><span class="korean">설레</span> - seolle (心動)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:#f9f9fc;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">你的學習進度</h2>
      <div class="progress-container">
        <div class="progress-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">248</span>
            個單字已掌握
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">17</span>
            天連續學習
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="badge">🏆 100單字大師徽章</div>
        <div class="badge" style="margin-left:12px;">🔥 熱血學習者</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2 class="section-title">準備好挑戰自己嗎？</h2>
      <a href="#" class="cta-btn">開始今日單字挑戰 →</a>
      <p style="margin-top:30px; color:#666; font-size:1.1rem;">
        完成每日挑戰，解鎖更多可愛貼圖與AI伴侶的甜甜稱讚 💕
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>讓每個單字都變成甜蜜回憶 • <span class="accent">공부하자</span> ♥ • 香港 K-learners • 2026</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
